cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.SE

The paper discusses the role of artificial intelligence and machine learning, which are both subfields of computer science. The focus on algorithmic computation and deep learning suggests cs.AI as the most likely sub-category. The discussion of complexity and the need to distinguish between artificial and living systems suggests cs.CC and cs.SY as additional likely sub-categories. The paper also touches on programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE) in its discussion of the role of machines in society.
